N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 191.8 - "fresh" not grade substitute

State Regulations

The use of the term "fresh" or any other term of similar
import shall not be deemed to be a substitute for grade designation. The term
"fresh" may not be applied to any lot of eggs which is below the requirements
for Grade A. Notes
